Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:11.28,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,618.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:23.00,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:26.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:30.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:33.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:36.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:40.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:44.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:48.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:54.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:59.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:15.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:19.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,140.389)}The Deadly Blood-Sucker!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx92\fs115\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,690.389)}Give It Your All, Rider Kid Corps
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure that I locked it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:20.16,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&}Operating Room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone! Someone come help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else in the hospital is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:03:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Woman... you're the only one left!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:08.85,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs50\c&H305516&}Kamen Rider \N{\c&H0F2592&}Kid Corps Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki and Mitsuru are now official\Nmembers of the Rider Kid Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:29.38,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H36ACB1&\3c&H305516&}Kamen Rider Kid Corps
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I pledge to fight Shocker,\Nto maintain peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and justice in our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it your best. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Choco.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Taki, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain? You're making me blush...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be bashful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then. My first act as Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're for sending messages\Namong the Kamen Rider Kid Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly straight, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we'll know the minute\NShocker tries something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're gonna be busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,5668. Is that your registration number?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tatsuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo, I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, I'm a member of\Nthe Kamen Rider Kid Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a security guard and you're a member\Nof the Kamen Rider Kid Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, give it your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you working tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The West Tokyo Blood Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, someone's been\Nstealing the precious blood
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,from blood banks in the area lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.89,0:05:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep the doors locked\Nand take care, too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:17.25,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an7\c&H080605&\3c&H43514A&}West Tokyo Blood Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... why in the world would\Nsomeone attack a blood bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a very good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the local hospitals are in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not enough blood for transfusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the blood in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, her shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you the only one without a shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it, then... did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood! Give me the blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this blood be enough
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to perform as many cyborg\Nsurgeries as we ask for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If I may, Ambassador,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it's best to use young\Nblood in our surgeries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The younger, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd prefer children's\Nblood, if we can get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Children's blood, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiraculas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Acquire children's blood\Nby any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When you drain a human's blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that person becomes your slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,See it done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The vampiric Shiraculas\Ncould suck human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:55.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's human hospital\Ncould then use that blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:57.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and the people he drained\Nwould become his slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He is a truly terrifying cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, kids! Gather 'round!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got nice things for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?\NHow about a caramel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's been gone a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd normally be back by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring more friends by to see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him take your blood, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you need to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're already friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you need to join Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how do you know about Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Tatsuo! Get in the\Nvan and let them take your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I'm out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo... let Shocker take your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, don't... don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo, listen to your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo! Tatsuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:09:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pigeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? There's no message...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He must not have had time to put one on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, investigate 5668.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... 5668...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider Kid Corps\Nmember Tatsuo Ito.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He lives in Oki Apartments 1-4.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check it out, Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, keep an eye out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's going on? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this one bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a ghost town in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared! A monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me suck your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:55.95,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi... I will suck your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shocker cyborg...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The vampiric Shiraculas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one drinking the blood\Nof the people here and controlling them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:13:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there any way to fix Taki\Nand the people of the apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could find the Shocker human hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'd have an\Nantidote there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Naoki and the others will\Nfind the Shocker blood donation van.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find the Shocker\Nblood donation van.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you find it, contact HQ\Nwith your pendants at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You check in with Mitsuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to do more searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing. Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got word from Naoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let Mr. Hongo know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't ride any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider! The Shocker van went that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. You've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You've served the Kamen\NRider Kid Corps well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.77,0:17:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Help Mr. Taki and the others quick, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Rider! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let them know I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be an antidote here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me... where is the\Nantidote to Shiraculas's venom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood is moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never get that antidote!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiraculas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Take this and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Give that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:28.69,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:31.82,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:35.82,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:39.38,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:42.95,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:46.58,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:49.06,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:52.50,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:57.43,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:21:00.78,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:11.86,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:14.68,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:19.11,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:22.63,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:26.27,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:29.30,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:32.35,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:36.11,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:40.76,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:43.76,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:55.29,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:58.14,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:22:02.46,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:06.03,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:09.71,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.71,0:22:12.98,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:15.82,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.95,0:22:19.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:24.23,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:27.83,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Dropkick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the Kamen Rider Kid Corps,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,do solemnly swear to continue our service.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:22:57.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The brave actions of Kamen Rider\Nand the Kamen Rider Kid Corps
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.24,0:22:59.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,put an end to Shocker's\Nbloodsucking monster, Shiraculas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.97,0:23:03.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But the planet was not\Nyet free of Shocker's evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:06.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go, Hongo Takeshi, the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:10.68,Cont,,0,60,155,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
