Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.71,0:23:16.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:20.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next week, I'm gonna invite\Nyou all to the house of terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:27.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You can enjoy watching the rose cyborg\NBararanga beat Kamen Rider to a pulp!
