Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:50.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.45,0:23:57.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.97,0:24:01.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.72,0:24:05.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.39,0:24:09.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.04,0:24:12.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Deadly Blood-Sucker!!\NGive It Your All, Rider Kid Corps
